author: Colin Packham
title: China says Australia parroting Trump with coronavirus criticism
description: China accused Australia of taking instructions from the United States over its criticism of Beijing's handling of the initial outbreak of the novel coronavirus, marking a further deterioration in ties between the two major trading partners.
content: SYDNEY (Reuters) - China accused Australia of taking instructions from the United States over its criticism of Beijing’s handling of the initial outbreak of the novel coronavirus, marking a further deterioration in ties between the two major trading partners.… [+2024 chars]
